      "message": "Converted to .graph(). But this is not important at all.\n\nNote that native() is a global stateless object populated during init() time. It can\u0027t have .graph as an attribute (since \u0027graph\u0027 is not global, but part of State{} struct that exists only temporary during \u0027Generate\u0027 call).",
